  The restat() is done in File::apply().

- handlecopyrename: after overwrite? -> no, then cursor is moved anyway

- (M)ore (S)how same dir: doesn't remove marks

- after (C)opy, the rcs status is not automatically added 

- when in (M)ore, the < key messes up the screen if the menu bar is
  scrolled to the extreme left

